snippet.textDisplay:
"O Raavi to Chenab phuchda ki haal hai satluj da":-How deeply  this verse of the song depicts the pain, sorrow and  grief of the people who suffer from the dreadful incident of partition  which was done by our cruel and ruthless politicians.
"O waaghe de border te raah phuchdi lahora de":- The grief and pain in this verse are deep.The pain of partition is only felt by those who are the victim of it.
Hats off to  to Jatinder Shah g for creating such a milestone track and expressing the pain, sorrow and  grief of the people in a soulful n heart touching way.This the beauty of music to express the feelings n emotion in a melodious way.
Politician always Sucks!:- then, now and forever.
